Architecture Note on License Compliance
==========================================================================

This MCP server (Apache-2.0) interacts with the above tools exclusively
through subprocess execution (child_process.execFile / CLI invocation).
There is no static or dynamic linking. Each tool runs as an independent
operating system process with communication limited to stdin/stdout text
streams. Under established open-source legal interpretation, this
constitutes "mere aggregation" and does not create a derivative work.

The Docker image bundles these tools for convenience. Users who
redistribute the Docker image should ensure compliance with each
component's license terms, particularly making source code available
for GPL/AGPL components upon request.
